ASTRAL
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
;
*DESCRIPTION_START
Dribbles of wax have spread out from the flickering candle which is the sole
illumination for this spartan chamber, sending lumpy tendrils across the
worn surface of the old desk. Ashes fill an unemptied incense bowl in one
corner of the desk. Scratched wantonly into the wooden surface are a few
basic incantations and some initials within a pierced heart. A simple bed can
be seen in reflection in the smudged mirror over the desk.
*DESCRIPTION_END

