*DESCRIPTION_START
Dank smells and cramped quarters give this small room an oppressive feel,
unalleviated by the dark, stained walls and the feeble light issuing from a
small slit in the exterior wall. In the dim glow an unkempt bed and low table
can be detected. A hypnotic pattern has been worked into the surface of the
well-worn table.
*DESCRIPTION_END

