NUMBER xxx
NAME Apprentice Quarters
REGION 15
CHANNEL 72
ASTRAL
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
;
*DESCRIPTION_START
An encircled mystic design surrounds a nauseating stain that mars the floor of 
this disturbing room. Unexplained chills caress the back of your neck
accompanied by the sensation of sounds that don't seem loud enough to be
heard. An alien aroma emanates from the direction of a bed that sags along the 
edges rather than the center, lending the air an unhealthy quality when you
inhale it. Strong iron bars in the small, high window seem designed to keep
something in, rather than keeping unwanted visitors out. Your sight can't
penetrate the shadows filling the corners of the room, yet it seems there's
something lurking somewhere close.
*DESCRIPTION_END 

; bed
