NUMBER xxx
NAME Mage's Laboratory
REGION 15
CHANNEL 72
ASTRAL
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
;
*DESCRIPTION_START
Books, crystals, rods, scrolls, flasks and unfinished snacks are strewn with
abandon about the laboratory on a myriad of shelves and available surface
space. The decaying desk and sagging work table exhibit the results of
countless experiments: some explosive, some messy, some smelly and some better 
left to the imagination. 
*DESCRIPTION_END

